47 SECTION 3.
48 Said article is further amended in Code Section 27-2-23, relating to license, permit, tag, and
49 stamp fees, by adding new subparagraphs to paragraph (1) to read as follows:
50 "(N) Resident Georgia turkey permit Annual 0.00
51 (O) Nonresident Georgia turkey permit Annual 100.00"
52 SECTION 4.
53 All laws and parts of laws in conflict with this Act are repealed.
